    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof, while the interior shows typical wear including some staining on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may require some minor maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
