    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a peerless example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a full Vanos system overhaul, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain operate at factory tolerances. The suspension maintains its original kinematic integrity, offering the telepathic steering response and balanced damping characteristic of a showroom-fresh vehicle. A true collector-grade machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
